summary: I’m starting to sound like a broken record, so I promise that this will be my last attempt. Thank you for putting up with me and...
caption:
I’m starting to sound like a broken record, so I promise that this will be my last attempt. Thank you for putting up with me and I’m really sorry for the repetition!

As some of you may know I lost my job a while back. I’m in a pretty tense situation right now as a result of that.
I need to save up some money and this is my last resort.

For right now, they are at a fixed price of $20 and $8+ for any additional characters. NSFW is okay!
However, I’m not willing to draw real people (sorry!) and I have little to no experience with furries, however I will try if I need to.
I also may charge more for complex props or armor, but only slightly.

If you’re interested or have any questions please feel free to message me here, or email me at mo0osquito0o@gmail.com .

Thank you for reading! Examples are below.
